With the reform of the organ law about the congress the two-party system is introduced, they deplore. 
Just the 60th legislative period had begun, and an opposition block, stated by the representatives of the PRD, PT, Convergencia and Jesús Manuel Patrón Montalvo who fancied as an independent already installed itself. Four questioned follower: the move of the 'two-party system' in the chamber. 
